{
  "stem": "14900.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "I knew I had to try and pass for 16.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "I don't know if that was the age, but that was the magical number.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "I probably weighed 70 pounds by then from malnutrition.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "I was not developed, maybe four feet seven or eight.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "But I had a piece of string with me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "And I tied my hair on the very end, in the back, then pulled it under and tied it around here into a pageboy that filled my face in.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "Don't ask me what I looked like, filthy, bedraggled, right-- three dresses which filled me out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "And when I got to the review committee I was so bound and determined, stood as straight as I could and I just smiled at them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know what made me do it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "With the flick of one finger [POINTS] my fate was decided.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He went to the right.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "I passed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "My mother passed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "We were in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "They marched us in, told us we were filthy, which of course we were.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 92,
      "text": "And we were going to be taken to the showers to get cleaned.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 93,
      "text": "By then, everybody knew what the showers meant.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 94,
      "text": "There were stories circling.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 95,
      "text": "Nobody could believe it, but we knew, even though you know the mind could not comprehend it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they marched us to the showers, told us to take all of our clothing off, that we would pick it up on the other side.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They'd fumigate it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We stood naked for a long time in a snake-like line.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember when I reached the end of that line and could see, there was a long, narrow room with mirrors on both sides, and chairs standing in front of these mirrors.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
